    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >### 愿望清单进度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16554 / 20000 [██████████████████░░░░] 83%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/d348ae032cf66527c3ac1488252bd025.avif?t=1771350433\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经 Pompasaur 批准 &gt;&gt;&gt; 灵感来自 Gnarled hag  <br>灵感来自 Gnarled Hag 和 Granny。你将扮演一个女孩，她需要逃出一个破旧的老房子，那里住着一个可怕的老爷爷。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >躲避他</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/83bf91a951970cf784a1295fba28d00b.poster.avif?t=1771350433\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/83bf91a951970cf784a1295fba28d00b.webm?t=1771350433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/83bf91a951970cf784a1295fba28d00b.mp4?t=1771350433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>躲在抽屉、箱子、沙发后面，寻找出路，但最重要的是不要发出声音。否则他会注意到你。你不想被他发现吧？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃离他的视线</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/247e9f732c4dc17cb5e626faf7a5d374.poster.avif?t=1771350433\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/247e9f732c4dc17cb5e626faf7a5d374.webm?t=1771350433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/247e9f732c4dc17cb5e626faf7a5d374.mp4?t=1771350433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你足够强壮，你还可以逃跑。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解谜</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/11895f670e0c968e51c9e852bf6e29de.poster.avif?t=1771350433\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/11895f670e0c968e51c9e852bf6e29de.webm?t=1771350433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/11895f670e0c968e51c9e852bf6e29de.mp4?t=1771350433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >房子很大，有很多陷阱和谜语要解开，才能找到出路。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/28092be2fb5d759306b5a4ef2eb7b045.poster.avif?t=1771350433\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/28092be2fb5d759306b5a4ef2eb7b045.webm?t=1771350433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111430/extras/28092be2fb5d759306b5a4ef2eb7b045.mp4?t=1771350433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是的，你得自己解决。</p>",
